ipxStatsTable.name: ipxStatsTable
ipxStatsTable.description: Provides a set of statistics for each IPX port. Each row (entry) of the table corresponds to a particular IPX port. Values in this table are read-only.

ipxStatsEntry.name: ipxStatsEntry
ipxStatsEntry.description: Provides a set of statistics for a particular IPX port.

ipxSysIndex.name: ipxSysIndex
ipxSysIndex.description: Identifies the number of an IPX port. This number is used as an index for this and the cxCfgIpxPortTable. Range of Values: 1 to 34 Default Value: None

ipxSysInReceives.name: ipxSysInReceives
ipxSysInReceives.description: Identifies the total number of IPX packets that have been received by this port. The sum includes those received in error. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysInHdrErrors.name: ipxSysInHdrErrors
ipxSysInHdrErrors.description: Identifies the number of IPX packets discarded due to errors in their headers. This number includes any IPX packet with a size less than the minimum of 30 bytes. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysInFiltered.name: ipxSysInFiltered
ipxSysInFiltered.description: Identifies the number of incoming packets that have been discarded due to filtering. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysInDiscards.name: ipxSysInDiscards
ipxSysInDiscards.description: Identifies the number of non-IPX packets received and discarded. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysForwPackets.name: ipxSysForwPackets
ipxSysForwPackets.description: Identifies the total number of IPX packets that have been forwarded by the port. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysOutFiltered.name: ipxSysOutFiltered
ipxSysOutFiltered.description: Identifies the number of outgoing IPX packets that have been discarded due to filtering. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysOutDiscards.name: ipxSysOutDiscards
ipxSysOutDiscards.description: Identifies the number of outgoing IPX packets discarded due to a formatting error. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysOutPackets.name: ipxSysOutPackets
ipxSysOutPackets.description: Identifies the total number of IPX packets transmitted by the port. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysResourceFailures.name: ipxSysResourceFailures
ipxSysResourceFailures.description: Identifies the number of times the IPX port has been unable to obtain needed resources, such as memory. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ripsapSysRIPIncorrectPackets.name: ripsapSysRIPIncorrectPackets
ripsapSysRIPIncorrectPackets.description: Identifies the number of times that the Port received an incorrectly formatted RIP packet Range of Values: 0 to 4,x294,x967,x295 Default Value: 0

ripsapSysSAPIncorrectPackets.name: ripsapSysSAPIncorrectPackets
ripsapSysSAPIncorrectPackets.description: Identifies the number of times that the IPX port received an incorrectly formatted SAP packet. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ripsapCircRIPOutPackets.name: ripsapCircRIPOutPackets
ripsapCircRIPOutPackets.description: Identifies the number of RIP packets sent by this IPX port. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ripsapCircRIPInPackets.name: ripsapCircRIPInPackets
ripsapCircRIPInPackets.description: Identifies the number of RIP packets received by this IPX port. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ripsapCircSAPOutPackets.name: ripsapCircSAPOutPackets
ripsapCircSAPOutPackets.description: Identifies the number of SAP packets sent by this IPX port Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ripsapCircSAPInPackets.name: ripsapCircSAPInPackets
ripsapCircSAPInPackets.description: Identifies the number of SAP packets received by this IPX port. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysWatchReq.name: ipxSysWatchReq
ipxSysWatchReq.description: Identifies the number of IPX Watchdog Request packets received on this port. Range of Values: 0 to 4, 294, 967, 295 Default Value: 0

ipxSysWatchRsp.name: ipxSysWatchRsp

ipxSysSerRcv.name: ipxSysSerRcv
